            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, pat your <strong>diced chicken breast</strong> dry and add them to a bowl with your <strong>cornflour</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> (freshly ground is best!), then toss to coat them evenly – this is your <strong>pepper chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1720448453334-x200.jpg",
