    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>in half lengthways, de-seed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop ﬁnely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong> finely</p>",
