    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped lemongrass inner core[s]</strong>, <strong>garlic</strong>, <strong>shallot</strong> and <strong>chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 2-4 min or until starting to crisp</p><p>Add your<strong> sugar snap peas</strong> and cook for a further 2-3 min</p>",
      "order": 6,
