      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>,<strong> rice vinegar</strong> and <strong>honey</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>hoisin mixture</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>hoisin mixture</strong> to the reserved pan over a medium heat</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until sticky – this is your<strong> sticky hoisin sauce</strong></p>",
