    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy pepper chicken</strong> with the<strong> sugar snap peas </strong>and<strong> lemongrass rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the<strong> sticky hoisin sauce</strong> over and sprinkle with your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
